                      </p>
                      <div class="ash-green-bg" style="line-height:1.5em;margin:2em 0;border:1px solid #bbb;border-radius:3px;padding:20px 20px 10px 20px;">
                        <p>
                          We have just opened up the program for enrollment and are sharing an early bird discount with you. Click on <%= link_to "this link", root_url(tracking: @tracking_info), target: "_blank" %> to get <span style="font-weight:bold">our starter package for ONLY <%= number_to_currency((Product.minimum(:price) - @promo.amount_discount), precision: 0) %>!</span>
                        </p>
                        <p>
