                          This discount is limited for the next <strong><%= @promo.duration %> ONLY</strong> and will end on <strong><%= @promo.end_date.to_s(:wday_month) %></strong>. Don't miss out on this great opportunity to update your practice and grow your profits.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                      <p>
                        The course will be starting on <%= @launch_date.to_s(:wday_month) %> (perfect timing to wrap up 2016 taxes and start prepping for Tax Day 2018!). You will continue to have access to the course even after it ends, so you can feel free to take some extra time to work through it or continue to reference the program materials at any time.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        Want to see more detailed course outline? Visit us <%= link_to "here", root_url(anchor: "program"), target: "_blank" %>.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        PS. What do you think ? This is not a marketing blast email. I’d really love to hear your thoughts and answer any questions you may have. So please feel free to drop me a line.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        Looking forward to helping you make the 2017-2018 your best tax season yet!
                      </p>
                      <br />
                      <p>
                        In service and gratitude,
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        - Marlon, Co-Pilot and Instructor at <a href="https://mymodernassets.com" target="_blank" style="color:#47b475;">Modern Assets</a>
                      </p>
                      <a href="https://mymodernassets.com" target="_blank" style="color:#47b475;">MyModernAssets.com</a>
